EDUCATIONAL USE NOTICE

This project was created solely for school and educational purposes.
It was created with the assistance of AI (Claude by Anthropic) and is
intended as a learning tool to help students understand the Subset Sum
dynamic programming algorithm through interactive visualization.

This software is not intended for commercial use or production deployment.
No academic integrity violation is implied or intended by the use of AI
assistance in generating this project — it is disclosed openly here and
in the README.
